{"id":"7640","name":"Decide For Me","tagline":"Makes a decision for you from a list of choices you provide.","icon":"ios14 c4271458815 g59723","latest":"24390","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>A shortcut that will make a decision for you from a list of choices you provide.</p>\n<p>Best used when run as a Run Shortcut action from another shortcut that way you can do things like \"Hey Siri, pick a board game\" or \"Hey Siri, what should I snack on?\"</p>\n<p>You can even add cooldowns so the same decision isn't repeatedly made.</p>\n<p>Learn more at <a href=\"https://shortcuts.toggleable.com/decide-for-me/instructions\">https://shortcuts.toggleable.com/decide-for-me/instructions</a></p>\n<p><img alt=\"decision made\" src=\"https://shortcuts.toggleable.com/decide-for-me/images/decision-small.jpg\" title=\"Decision made\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"main menu\" src=\"https://shortcuts.toggleable.com/decide-for-me/images/main-menu-small.jpg\" title=\"Main menu\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"editing choices\" src=\"https://shortcuts.toggleable.com/decide-for-me/images/edit-choices-small.jpg\" title=\"Editing choices\"></p>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>1.4.0 - Jan. 9, 2021, 3:43 p.m.</strong></p><p>- You can now change how often a cooldown is adjusted after accepting a decision. By default, there is no delay, meaning choices on cooldown will be adjusted immediately. You have the option of limiting the adjustment to once per day, per hour, or per minute.<br>- The date and time will now be displayed when showing your last decision. For items with a 0 cooldown period, you'll need to make another decision before a date and time appear.<br>- Use a check image to show which setting is selected instead of a generic gear icon.<br>- Use SF Symbols for icon glyphs.<br>- Move settings to dedicated submenu.<br>- Changed import question to show instructions on how to create a shortcut to use different decision sets.</p>"}